        <mxCell id="qcXrrN8o2vu8g5xNh5Mg-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="ODD - design an instagram like system with following reqs&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;1. user login service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. content service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. feed service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. follower Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5.&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;User engagement service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;implement a mechanism to restrict the user fro posting a non policy complaint post&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;optmiize the dynamix deed generation for the users&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;highlight the use of backfill service&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
